  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This case-control study investigated B-vitamin and homocysteine in relation to the presence
      or the absence of type 2 diabetes and clinical signs of polyneuropathy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Blood samples were collected and clinical investigations were performed at the same time.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
